	This wonderful soap slice is blended together with pure essential oils, giving an aromatic blend of zesty limes and black pepper. Renowned for their stimulating properties this soap is sure to revive the senses and reawaken your spirit.&nbsp;This fantastic soap can be used like any normal bar of soap but is much milder. Simply rub the bar repeatedly between wet hands until you form a lather to clean your skin with or alternatively, rub the bar onto a sponge. Due to the soap being hand made the pattern in the soap may vary slightly from the one pictured.</p>
